### **4. 37_LiveMetricScope**  
**Description:**  
Live-stream chart visualizer for real-time data feeds or performance metrics.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveMetricScope - Real-Time Data Chart Viewer

LiveMetricScope displays streaming numerical input as a smooth, real-time line chart for metrics, simulations, or dashboards.

## Features
- Realtime updates  
- Auto-scroll chart  
- Matplotlib-powered  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_LiveMetricScope.git
cd 37_LiveMetricScope
python visualize.py
